{"tid":1333182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投下啦不如]  幾多人當721係最後一次？","createTime":"2019-07-19T14:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T16:15:39.000Z","uid":249040,"like":17,"dislike":138,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"31a244df7389d2b47b741e8a6f6251057c54fcaf","tid":1333182,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:59:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">利申： 不是投任何現場部署，留番到時傾<br />\n<br />\n時代雜誌話咩我地有直接民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實到時邊投到票呀  網上定現場都好<br />\n<br />\n宜家個情況又嚴峻左咁多，今日唔知聽日事，不如趁仲有少少時間大家互相知下大家點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n少數個邊唔洗服從多數，今日位巴打講得啱，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認同最大嘅改變最終由少數人黎推動！但到宜家，如果大部分人 都唔知個小部份人到時會點考慮</span></span>，咁完左721後個分歧會唔會出現？<br />\n我地好需要長期一齊行呢條路！ <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">㩒讚 like：<br />\n係最後今次！ 你冇撚病呀？！以後食粥食飯睇今舖！ <br />\n㩒彈 dislike：<br />\n唔係最後一次，我已經當人生馬拉松咁長期抗爭<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">（銀絲睇得明嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n再次利申：唔想投咪算...我係諗其實大家都想得個知字啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />費事到時兵荒馬亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"c43b34ff28dc592aa1ee5442d9e1cdd18ad2a66b","tid":1333182,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc0c18dc1bda38ca9d0ebbbd2c6a3fe467137774","tid":1333182,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:01:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d5b63ef5379315c3641953f706797f723dc4ad6d","tid":1333182,"uid":63639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:02:36.000Z","msg":"投唔落"},{"pid":"772282926391666a969597f12bec7d3edc29233e","tid":1333182,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:03: